_margin_bottom":"0px","mb_margin_top":"0px","mb_margin_bottom":"0px"}},"16475044893a95f2ba":{"type":"graphic-module","blocks":{"164750448965bcfeac-0":{"type":"slide","settings":{"icon":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/953ebbc1f2f5775c228625e1c716cf87_3a7d0f42-a157-4aca-92da-cc27440cd9ae.png","main_title":"750W","text":"Rear Hub Motor"}},"164750448965bcfeac-1":{"type":"slide","settings":{"icon":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/dcbf258b7e33f36ca3423eee233866fa_eb6fa8ca-140c-453c-9769-0765dd5dbc08.png","main_title":"85N.m","text":"Motor Torque"}},"164750448965bcfeac-2":{"type":"slide","settings":{"icon":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/c5b9a1702888b8b61400b8ec135d2fdf_638b2fc2-1c3a-4eff-a71c-65c68786a640.png","main_title":"48V -13 Ah","text":"Lithium-lon Battery"}},"164750448965bcfeac-3":{"type":"slide","settings":{"icon":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/92ccb5073072aeb08280d30f5618bb0c_4940464d-a479-40a9-a6d2-34eaacc6e346.png","main_title":"300 lbs","text":"Payload Capacity"}}},"block_order":["164750448965bcfeac-0","164750448965bcfeac-1","164750448965bcfeac-2","164750448965bcfeac-3"],"settings":{"max_width":"1400px","main_image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/471b564f8f0ca7b2b1c0b43f6998d000.jpg","pc_margin_top":"50px","pc_margin_bottom":"0px","mb_margin_top":"0px","mb_margin_bottom":"0px"}},"16475044927aaa8afe":{"type":"slide-bar","blocks":{"164750449242ef9e47-0":{"type":"slide","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/DSC_5949.jpg","text":"<strong>Hidden wiring<\/strong><br>The wiring of MF-18 P is hidden wiring, hidden in the frame with a unique design. Make the overall appearance of the vehicle even more beautiful. At the same time, hidden wiring also greatly reduces the exposure of the wires and prevents the wires from being damaged due to external factors."}},"164750449242ef9e47-1":{"type":"slide","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/DSC_5909.jpg","text":"<strong>Suspension Front Fork <\/strong><br>We developed and produced Maxfoot suspension forks in cooperation with well-known manufacturers. While ensuring beautiful design, we pay more attention to the rider's experience. The long-distance suspension stroke allows the MF-18 P to filter out most of the bumps, ensuring a comfortable riding experience for the rider. Therefore, with the Maxfoot suspension fork, the MF-18 P can conquer many terrains."}},"164750449242ef9e47-2":{"type":"slide","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/DSC_6082.jpg","text":"<strong>Thoughtful Big Curved Handlebar <\/strong><br>Curved Handlebar aluminum handlebars allow adjustment to support various arm lengths and a more laid back riding position. During riding, the curved handlebar allows the rider to ride in a comfortable position. you will not feel uncomfortable because of the sitting position even when traveling long distances."}},"7793197b-732a-4d46-83d2-dfa25e924558":{"type":"slide","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/DSC_6037_5d7a4cab-1db1-4403-aa66-0a9a33efd3ce.jpg","text":"<strong>Thick Padded Saddle, Designed For Comfort <\/strong><br>Adjustable thick Padded Saddle can greatly alleviate your discomfort caused by a long journey and all-round buffering allows you to feel what is the comfortable riding. You can adjust it according to the height. Appropriate height for this bike is 5'4''-6'3''."}},"dbf8d43f-b3d5-4841-830f-6491e2002371":{"type":"slide","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/DSC_6064.jpg","text":"<strong>Maxfoot 750W Hub Motor<\/strong><br>The motor of MF-18 P is Maxfoot motor developed by Maxfoot and a well-known manufacturer. While guaranteeing the quality of the motor, it also improves the performance of the motor. At a rated power of 750W, the Maxfoot motor can output at least 1050W of power. There will be no security risks due to its high performance."}},"8eef4b88-bbb3-40d3-9766-77e566604293":{"type":"slide","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/DSC_5972.jpg","text":"<strong>Maxfoot Lithium Battery<\/strong><br>In order to ensure the long-range of the MF-18 P, Maxfoot teamed up with well-known manufacturers to develop a 13Ah Maxfoot large-capacity battery. As the energy support of MF-18 P, we attach great importance to its quality. We need to ensure that it does not have any safety risks while providing energy. Therefore, the Maxfoot battery is a very successful battery."}}},"block_order":["164750449242ef9e47-0","164750449242ef9e47-1","164750449242ef9e47-2","7793197b-732a-4d46-83d2-dfa25e924558","dbf8d43f-b3d5-4841-830f-6491e2002371","8eef4b88-bbb3-40d3-9766-77e566604293"],"disabled":true,"settings":{"max_width":"1400px","pc_margin_top":"50px","pc_margin_bottom":"0px","mb_margin_top":"0px","mb_margin_bottom":"0px"}},"166244556805353f49":{"type":"multicolumn","blocks":{"1662445567a77f6eed-0":{"type":"column","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/DSC_5949_33295177-52ae-4ab2-be80-7a8a503c95e9.jpg","title":"Hidden wiring","text":"<p>The wiring of MF-18 P is hidden wiring, hidden in the frame with a unique design. Make the overall appearance of the vehicle even more beautiful. At the same time, hidden wiring also greatly reduces the exposure of the wires and prevents the wires from being damaged due to external factors.<\/p>","link_label":"","link":""}},"1662445567a77f6eed-1":{"type":"column","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/DSC_5909_6bb1eb77-e8d8-4828-988d-c7334365a1b5.jpg","title":"Suspension Front Fork","text":"<p>We developed and produced Maxfoot suspension forks in cooperation with well-known manufacturers. While ensuring beautiful design, we pay more attention to the rider's experience. The long-distance suspension stroke allows the MF-18 P to filter out most of the bumps, ensuring a comfortable riding experience for the rider. <\/p>","link_label":"","link":""}},"1662445567a77f6eed-2":{"type":"column","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/DSC_6082_b58bf521-dddd-4e47-8408-cef5bbcc1c3c.jpg","title":"Thoughtful Big Curved Handlebar","text":"<p>Curved Handlebar aluminum handlebars allow adjustme